  <summary date="2021-04-07T14:14:30Z" status="Introduced in House">Supplemental Security Income Restoration Act of 2019

This bill modifies the Supplemental Security Income (SSI) benefits program by (1) excluding certain income and raising the resource limit for purposes of determining SSI eligibility, (2) providing for annual inflation adjustments for benefits, and (3) repealing certain SSI penalties related to disposing of resources for less than fair market value.</summary>
